title: Kızılcabölük, Tavas
content:
Kızılcabölük is a neighbourhood of the municipality and district of Tavas, Denizli Province, Turkey.[1][2] Its population is 3,392 (2022).[3] Before the 2013 reorganisation, it was a town (belde).[4][5]
